{"tid":433032,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[漫畫推介]有冇人有睇井上雄彥 Real?","createTime":"2017-10-12T04:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T04:09:37.000Z","uid":102676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a848935e7a66447d92c04b81804706c534b8454","tid":433032,"uid":102676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"作為一套漫畫 有別於一般漫畫 Real同佢既名一樣用現實去打動讀者<br />\n<br />\n開頭以為井上又出運動漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要未曾接觸過既輪椅籃球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知睇睇下發覺唔對路 <br />\n好似仲正過一般運動漫畫！<br />\n<br />\n成個故事都係圍繞住三個主角户川 野宮 同高橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/115823_3c19e99fcd76063d9b156d0d6938f075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F115823_3c19e99fcd76063d9b156d0d6938f075.jpg&h=922b2190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n户川清春 係一個好勝心極強既人 讀書時係一個極有將來既短跑新星 即使疾病令佢失去左隻腳 都冇令佢感到自卑 甚至覺得係籃球上佢唔會輸俾一個正常人<br />\n但亦都係呢種好勝心同自尊心令佢同隊友之間經常有磨擦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/120819_f100f56f0560702579d86d5f75ea3625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F120819_f100f56f0560702579d86d5f75ea3625.jpg&h=be1f60fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n野宮朋美 放棄左籃球 走左去同豬朋狗友玩樂 直至發生意外 害到一個女仔要坐一世輪椅 同埋遇到户川 佢開始意識到自己需要改變<br />\n個人黎講最鍾意呢個角色 因為佢就好似好多人咁 有後悔既野 想自己努力作出改變 想追返自己miss左既野 但係現實就係 人地未必會俾機會你 失去左既野又未必追得返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/122557_a32e39e7069fe27ad63393798964e5b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F122557_a32e39e7069fe27ad63393798964e5b8.jpg&h=d98c3ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高橋久信 有天賦既籃球員 同野宮曾經係隊友 有過d過節  做任何野都比人容易上手 無論係讀書定係籃球 都輕易地做得俾其他人好 就因為咁 努力似乎唔係佢人生既字典度<br />\n但係之後既劇情中 佢既人生出現左巨變 所有野都唔同哂 而佢就因此而不得不改變自己<br />\n<br />\n基本上係漫畫入面既每一個人都有自己大大小小既困難 就好似現實中既每一個人都係度掙扎求存 一切都好似發生係現實既某個角落咁 最好睇既就係睇佢地點樣去受挫而又點樣去面對 因為畢竟大家都只係一個人"},{"pid":"2f67168b65faae26c1a4e509f6de2ed9e754381b","tid":433032,"uid":56498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時追完浪客行就係追呢套<br />\n<br />\n連埋sd全部都好有男人的浪漫"},{"pid":"285a87959f42b31a293f6da91bd68e09d17d1a25","tid":433032,"uid":11159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"可惜休刊左好耐"},{"pid":"4db702c19d129319de91831137fd88b9d924ed32","tid":433032,"uid":102676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時追完浪客行就係追呢套<br />\n<br />\n連埋sd全部都好有男人的浪漫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最可惜係兩套都等緊佢出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇睇下覺得real實在太感動到人"},{"pid":"66305cf4059ecf414050b910a1d377a382c354ac","tid":433032,"uid":102676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可惜休刊左好耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前睇過專訪都有講其實井上都好有要求<br />\n會坐係個咖啡廳度諗下d人物會點做<br />\n感覺上好似同緊角色對話咁 所以有時都用好多時間<br />\n不過咁既質素係值得等既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝井上大師長命百歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f565cd22aef9b0f0cacade802fc4d4d074c57a","tid":433032,"uid":32946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"想知切5一幅圖下面果隻公仔係出自邊本漫畫?<br />\n細個好似係EXAM入面睇過"},{"pid":"1f4f1d456c48a5e84e46788a7a3f69cadcdaed94","tid":433032,"uid":54066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cf057bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成本野重深印象係呢個彩蛋"},{"pid":"d8e153f051e574a9b1f2b737ea10e76f24954a26","tid":433032,"uid":57489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:37:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cf057bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成本野重深印象係呢個彩蛋</blockquote><br />\n印象中花道(はなみち)有康莊大道既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該用左雙關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83901d98df26206cba6a64a88237dc53f7c6384","tid":433032,"uid":102676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cf057bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成本野重深印象係呢個彩蛋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔知有呢個彩蛋<br />\n雖然樓上都有講係雙關 但見到都幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2deb83a86525dff24db2ddec856f646ceb98b0f","tid":433032,"uid":17528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a83901d98df26206cba6a64a88237dc53f7c6384","tid":433032,"uid":102676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F153028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cf057bec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成本野重深印象係呢個彩蛋</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係唔知有呢個彩蛋<br />\n雖然樓上都有講係雙關 但見到都幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:09:37.000Z","msg":"仲有冇出<br />\n好想睇埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}